[normal]Written evidence submitted by the [bold]National Union of Journalists (N[bold]UJ) [WAS0019][bold]&#xa0;
[normal]The National Union of Journalists is the voice for journalism and for journalists in the UK and Ireland, representing all sectors of the media, including freelances, casuals and staff in newspapers, news agencies, broadcasting, magazines, online, book publishing, in public relations and photographers. 
